StoreProvider<T>
public class PerHttpSessionStoreProvider<T>
extends AbstractPerXStoreProvider<T>

A StoreProvider that allows us to have a number of StoreProviders for each HttpSession. New StoreProviders are created by a StoreProviderFactory and stored in the HttpSession under a given attribute name.
